&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;uninstall&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;Uninstall&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;an&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;Update&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;apps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;or&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;Scoop&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;itself&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;virustotal&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;Look&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;s hash on virustotal.com
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;which       Locate a shim/executable (similar to &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;which&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39; on Linux)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;Type &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;scoop&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;command&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;specific&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;command&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
